    "title": "SIERRA Black",
    "body_html": "- **Description:**Sporty yet refined, Sierra delivers on both comfort and support. With our high arch Momentum footbed, this versatile shoe targets plantar fasciitis and heel spurs. A reliable pick for every day, whether you're on your feet or on the move.\n    \n    This style is a C+/D width. These styles are a D width, with the option to be worn as a C+ width. To create a C+ width (more snug fit), slip the Vari-fit innersole (found in your shoe box) under the existing footbed.\n    \n    Homyped has been designing footwear in Australia since 1969, making us the original orthopaedic comfort shoe specialist. We cater to sizes 5 to 11 (some including half sizes) and widths from medium to extra wide. Our footbeds are designed with your feet in mind, while targeting common foot conditions such as bunions, heel spurs, plantar fasciitis, arthritis, swollen feet, and diabetic feet. Step into unapparelled comfort and experience the Homyped difference.\n- **Features:**\n- **Sizing &amp; Fitting:**\n- **Material:**\n- **Wellness Condition:**\n- **Shipping:****Free Shipping**\n    \n    Free shipping is available on all orders within Australia over $120 AUD.\n    \n    A flat rate of $12 AUD (Inc. GST) postage will be charged for any order less than $120 AUD.\n    \n    **Delivery**\n    \n    Estimated 5-7 Business Days in Metro Addresses.\n    \n    Estimated 4-9 Business Days in Regional Addresses.",
